        {"heading": "Popular Next Steps", "content": "<p>Most readers should continue into one of these decisions: whether their symptoms justify a sleep study, whether a home sleep apnea test is enough, what to do if CPAP is not working, how oral appliances compare, when Inspire is relevant, and whether sleep apnea is contributing to weight gain or poor metabolic markers.</p>"},
